LEARN FROM THEM, AND GROW.

237
00:16:01,416 --> 00:16:05,458
- OKAY. I UNDERSTAND, THANKS.

238
00:16:05,541 --> 00:16:09,583
HEY, RYOSUKE, THEY'RE SAYING
FUJIWARA JUST GOT PASSED.

239
00:16:09,666 --> 00:16:13,000
( sighs ) I GUESS
THAT'S THE END OF IT.

240
00:16:13,083 --> 00:16:15,458
HE'S DONE GOOD UP TO NOW,
BUT IT'S OVER.

241
00:16:15,541 --> 00:16:17,375
- THE GUY MADE A SMOOTH MOVE
AND OWNED IT.

242
00:16:17,458 --> 00:16:18,791
